        public boolean isOutputHostname()

      • setExpireInterval

        public void setExpireInterval(String interval)
        Set the interval based on the format: e${expireInterval:long}${expireIntervalUnit:character}.
        expireIntervalUnit:
        • s - second
        • m - minute
        • h - hour
        • d - day
        Example "e1h" - expire in 1 hour.
        Parameters:
        interval - the interval.

      • setOutputHostname

        Parameters:
        outputHostname - the output hostname flag.
